Melt 2 Saute Express(R) squares in 10-inch nonstick skillet over medium-low heat just until bubbles begin to form. Add chicken. Saute 13-18 minutes or until chicken is golden brown on both sides and done (165 degrees F). Remove from skillet. Cut into thin strips. Melt remaining 1 Saute Express(R) square in skillet. Add bell peppers and onion. Cook 5-7 minutes or until softened. Heat refried beans in microwave until warm. Spread over tortillas. Top each tortilla with chicken, pepper mixture, cheese and additional toppings.